VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT \b(system|popen|_popen)\s*\(
WHEN EXPR MISSING:validate|sanitize|allowlist|QStringList\s*\(\s*\{|QProcess::startDetached && MISSING:test|example
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects OS command execution APIs in C++ code paths.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for Qt Command Execution Sink.
